          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_Published_EnergyChangeReportAllFacilities",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to generate a report on energy consumption changes across all facilities for a specified billing period. It logs the usage of the report, calculates energy consumption metrics for both the current and prior fiscal years, and retrieves data for facilities associated with specified agencies. The procedure is part of a reporting system, likely used for auditing or monitoring energy usage trends."
        }
      ]
    },
